            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the green stalks off the <strong>aubergines</strong> and cut each aubergine, lengthways into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12] </span>wedges</p><p>Thread 6 <strong>aubergine wedges</strong> onto 2 <strong>skewers</strong>, alternating between flesh and skin side up until you have a rack of aubergine</p><p>Repeat with the <strong>remaining aubergine wedges</strong> and <strong>remaining skewers</strong> until you end up with 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> <strong>aubergine racks</strong></p>",
